Sanitize @cheese cloth{} if necessary by pouring boiling water over it.

Mix @yoghurt{1%Kg} @water{0.5%l} @salt{1%tbsp} and let drain over night in the fridge (spread cloth into sieve over bowl and fill with yoghurt mix).

Transfer mix using a spoon to a suitable vessel.

Mix in @mint, finely cut @garlic, thinly sliced or powder{} to taste. 

Cover with @olive oil{} oil.
